00:16:22.770 --> 00:16:24.200
Leave with my brothers

00:16:25.120 --> 00:16:26.440
and hide them for the time being.

00:16:27.440 --> 00:16:27.840
But

00:16:28.090 --> 00:16:29.090
what about that guy?

00:16:29.530 --> 00:16:30.570
He did kill all the familiar members

00:16:30.570 --> 00:16:32.290
of the deceased physicians.

00:16:33.120 --> 00:16:35.070
If we can't get him what he wants,

00:16:35.070 --> 00:16:36.480
- then... - Then not only will we die,

00:16:38.070 --> 00:16:39.790
but family members of all physicians in Shangyi

00:16:41.030 --> 00:16:42.230
will meet their miserable fate.

00:16:42.830 --> 00:16:43.480
Leader,

00:16:43.990 --> 00:16:45.440
should we...

00:16:48.200 --> 00:16:49.650
We'll have to move fast

00:16:51.720 --> 00:16:53.110
for the sake of all those innocent lives.

00:16:58.640 --> 00:16:59.640
Time to go!

00:16:59.640 --> 00:17:00.570
Hold on!

00:17:00.850 --> 00:17:01.680
Who's standing in the way?

00:17:03.400 --> 00:17:04.910
I need to talk to your boss.

00:17:05.630 --> 00:17:06.380
Stop!

00:17:08.770 --> 00:17:09.440
Guys,

00:17:09.850 --> 00:17:10.870
let's not get rough here.

00:17:15.520 --> 00:17:17.170
I apologize for the tension.

00:17:17.520 --> 00:17:19.480
Our caravan encountered bandits before,

00:17:19.720 --> 00:17:20.850
that's why the guys

00:17:20.850 --> 00:17:22.060
has been vigilant lately.

00:17:23.530 --> 00:17:25.210
You must be their young master.

00:17:25.570 --> 00:17:26.370
Yours truly.

00:17:26.930 --> 00:17:29.360
Are you the one who sold all those medicines

00:17:29.360 --> 00:17:30.500
with low prices in Shangyi?

00:17:30.550 --> 00:17:32.440
Our caravan was looted

00:17:32.650 --> 00:17:34.880
and all our medicines were lost.

00:17:35.180 --> 00:17:37.290
The medicines must have come from them.

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:39.350
Your caravan

00:17:39.350 --> 00:17:40.650
is fully staffed.

00:17:40.930 --> 00:17:42.760
How did the bandits pull it off so easily?

00:17:43.960 --> 00:17:45.600
You don't know the whole truth.

00:17:46.440 --> 00:17:48.440
The bandits have excellent combat skills

00:17:48.690 --> 00:17:50.160
and are well organized.

00:17:50.330 --> 00:17:52.850
They retreated in an instant after they got the medicines.

00:17:53.680 --> 00:17:55.790
My security head didn't get to chase them.

00:17:56.610 --> 00:17:58.000
They are not new to this.

00:17:58.270 --> 00:18:00.440
I did notice that the bandit leader

00:18:00.720 --> 00:18:03.330
was wearing heavy armor.

00:18:03.520 --> 00:18:05.410
He doesn't seem to be an ordinary bandit.

00:18:07.690 --> 00:18:09.130
I don't think the answer

00:18:09.410 --> 00:18:10.330
is too complicated.

00:18:11.040 --> 00:18:12.330
Zhao Sihu, one of the four pests,

00:18:12.760 --> 00:18:14.130
is the only one with a team

00:18:14.130 --> 00:18:15.200
equipped with horses.

00:18:15.610 --> 00:18:17.330
I think we just need to find him

00:18:17.610 --> 00:18:18.690
and ask him in person.

00:18:24.070 --> 00:18:25.920
Why haven't the bandits come yet?

00:18:28.390 --> 00:18:29.790
Are you sure they're here?

00:18:30.490 --> 00:18:31.700
It can't be.

00:18:33.260 --> 00:18:34.000
They should

00:18:34.000 --> 00:18:35.840
have arrived by now.

00:18:36.000 --> 00:18:37.070
You mean those masked men,

00:18:37.470 --> 00:18:38.440
the bandits,

00:18:38.890 --> 00:18:40.600
always rob along this road?

00:18:41.440 --> 00:18:43.120
You are just sitting back and waiting.

00:18:56.990 --> 00:18:58.160
Here they are.

00:19:06.980 --> 00:19:07.980
It took so long.

00:19:08.430 --> 00:19:09.400
We're here.

00:19:10.430 --> 00:19:11.030
Here.

00:19:29.960 --> 00:19:30.840
We're friends.

00:19:31.030 --> 00:19:32.600
I thought he had some tricks.

00:19:32.640 --> 00:19:34.080
But he's just a fool.

00:19:35.400 --> 00:19:36.200
What's going on?

00:19:36.440 --> 00:19:36.870
Gu Tian.

00:19:41.640 --> 00:19:43.230
If you have anything to save your life, take it.

00:19:44.600 --> 00:19:45.540
Are you okay?

00:19:46.130 --> 00:19:46.620
Move.

00:19:49.700 --> 00:19:51.140
When County Magistrate Yang sees this,

00:19:51.140 --> 00:19:52.190
he will know I'm in danger

00:19:52.190 --> 00:19:53.540
and the backup will be here soon.

00:19:56.830 --> 00:19:58.540
You think we can hold that long?

00:20:02.380 --> 00:20:03.070
We are friends.

00:20:03.070 --> 00:20:03.830
Don't...

00:20:05.890 --> 00:20:06.630
Sorry.

00:20:28.990 --> 00:20:29.830
It's you.

00:20:40.840 --> 00:20:43.020
The armor! You are the fake bandit who stole the herbs.

00:20:44.220 --> 00:20:45.220
I will die anyway,

00:20:45.390 --> 00:20:47.190
so does it matter who kills me?

00:20:47.190 --> 00:20:47.950
Let's go.

00:20:48.010 --> 00:20:48.780
Forward!

00:20:51.430 --> 00:20:51.920
Let's go.

00:20:51.920 --> 00:20:52.460
Retreat!

00:20:57.710 --> 00:20:59.540
They're not Shangyi's rescuers.

00:20:59.540 --> 00:21:00.870
They're real bandits.

00:21:01.660 --> 00:21:03.390
What should we do?

00:21:05.830 --> 00:21:08.020
Long time no see, Crazy Fu.

00:21:08.950 --> 00:21:10.510
Didn't expect you would have this day.

00:21:11.660 --> 00:21:13.020
Dismount and take off your clothes.

00:21:24.460 --> 00:21:27.980
[Zhao Sihu]

00:21:35.760 --> 00:21:36.560
Nice.

00:21:37.350 --> 00:21:39.750
I should have seen you again yesterday.

00:21:39.830 --> 00:21:41.590
But I was occupied.

00:21:42.220 --> 00:21:43.780
How are you feeling these days?

00:21:44.990 --> 00:21:46.070
Feel the same.

00:21:46.510 --> 00:21:48.460
I can't get the energy to do anything.

00:21:50.390 --> 00:21:51.780
Not even interested in robbing people.

00:21:52.190 --> 00:21:53.950
If I hadn't heard that

00:21:54.100 --> 00:21:55.580
you had this problem,

00:21:56.070 --> 00:21:58.050
I would be drinking in the village right now.

00:21:58.420 --> 00:21:59.620
You're drinking again?

00:22:02.860 --> 00:22:04.130
No, I'm not.

00:22:04.130 --> 00:22:04.940
I just

00:22:05.060 --> 00:22:07.250
took a little sip.

00:22:08.090 --> 00:22:09.740
You can ask them.

00:22:11.010 --> 00:22:12.060
How much did he drink?

00:22:19.820 --> 00:22:20.980
No, stop.

00:22:20.980 --> 00:22:22.650
Easy.

00:22:25.180 --> 00:22:26.330
Stop yelling.

00:22:27.250 --> 00:22:28.210
Listen.

00:22:28.620 --> 00:22:30.300
The heart is to circulate blood,

00:22:30.450 --> 00:22:32.060
and the liver is to keep it.

00:22:32.880 --> 00:22:34.510
This liver conflicts with alcohol.

00:22:35.000 --> 00:22:36.680
Your internal organs are already at the end of their strength.

00:22:36.920 --> 00:22:38.480
If you still don't listen to me,

00:22:38.590 --> 00:22:39.860
you won't survive the end of the month.

00:22:40.540 --> 00:22:42.020
This life is your own.

00:22:42.700 --> 00:22:45.460
But when you go out, don't tell others

00:22:45.460 --> 00:22:46.780
that I saved you.

00:22:46.830 --> 00:22:47.990
I can't afford to lose face.

00:22:48.020 --> 00:22:50.780
I told you I had palpitations and couldn't breathe.

00:22:51.100 --> 00:22:53.020
But you aimed at my liver.

00:22:53.780 --> 00:22:56.950
If your liver is damaged, your heart will also be affected.

00:22:57.140 --> 00:22:58.950
That's why I don't let you drink, okay?

00:22:58.950 --> 00:23:00.940
Alright, alright.

00:23:01.780 --> 00:23:02.590
Crazy Fu.

00:23:03.270 --> 00:23:04.060
No.

00:23:04.470 --> 00:23:05.180
Physician Fu.

00:23:05.470 --> 00:23:06.590
I saved you.

00:23:06.590 --> 00:23:07.710
So

00:23:07.900 --> 00:23:09.140
you won't charge me, right?

00:23:09.140 --> 00:23:09.870
Sure.

00:23:10.870 --> 00:23:12.270
It's not fair.

00:23:12.590 --> 00:23:14.630
It's fine. His words make sense.

00:23:14.870 --> 00:23:16.710
Are you silly?

00:23:16.710 --> 00:23:18.270
Who do you think you are?

00:23:19.000 --> 00:23:20.990
These people are kidnapping and extorting people

00:23:20.990 --> 00:23:22.110
under your name.

00:23:22.110 --> 00:23:22.850
If it weren't for us,

00:23:22.850 --> 00:23:24.100
you would have been blamed.

00:23:25.150 --> 00:23:26.630
So this time you saved us

00:23:26.630 --> 00:23:27.820
and it can be even,

00:23:27.860 --> 00:23:29.390
but you should pay him

00:23:29.390 --> 00:23:30.430
for the treatment.

00:23:33.100 --> 00:23:34.940
This is the first time

00:23:35.150 --> 00:23:36.630
I've heard of such a thing.

00:23:37.310 --> 00:23:38.820
Take them back

00:23:39.270 --> 00:23:40.510
and torture them.

00:23:40.790 --> 00:23:42.060
I want to see

00:23:42.340 --> 00:23:43.220
who has the guts

00:23:43.460 --> 00:23:45.180
to do this.

00:23:45.270 --> 00:23:45.980
Here.

00:23:47.860 --> 00:23:48.430
Leader.

00:23:48.630 --> 00:23:50.030
Troops from Shangyi are coming soon.

00:23:55.940 --> 00:23:56.750
Guys.

00:23:58.180 --> 00:23:59.220
Farewell.

00:24:02.030 --> 00:24:02.510
Let's go.

00:24:05.340 --> 00:24:07.460
No wonder you dared to meet Zhao Sihu.

00:24:07.790 --> 00:24:09.790
You two had such a connection.

00:24:10.940 --> 00:24:12.580
I repaid the favor Zhao Sihu did

00:24:12.580 --> 00:24:13.910
for saving us today,

00:24:13.910 --> 00:24:14.910
so you two

00:24:14.910 --> 00:24:16.580
should also owe me a favor.

00:24:17.200 --> 00:24:18.860
Now you become smart.

00:24:19.050 --> 00:24:19.750
Fine.

00:24:19.940 --> 00:24:21.470
But my favor is valuable,

00:24:21.470 --> 00:24:22.020
don't waste it.

00:24:22.020 --> 00:24:22.780
I know.

00:24:25.030 --> 00:24:25.950
Physician Fu.

00:24:26.250 --> 00:24:28.230
I almost forgot your father's instructions.

00:24:28.550 --> 00:24:30.090
He asked me to give this to you.

00:24:33.340 --> 00:24:34.150
Bye.

00:24:37.670 --> 00:24:38.510
What's this?

00:24:39.430 --> 00:24:40.670
My father's medical book.

00:24:40.700 --> 00:24:42.430
I left it there.

00:24:45.750 --> 00:24:46.320
Sir.

00:24:46.680 --> 00:24:48.080
This time we are defeated.

00:24:48.230 --> 00:24:49.750
This is the first time we've lost so many men.

00:24:51.470 --> 00:24:52.020
Go.

00:24:53.550 --> 00:24:55.240
Block all the intersections in Shangyi.

00:24:55.550 --> 00:24:57.080
As long as this person is in Shangyi,

00:24:57.750 --> 00:24:58.790
we have a chance.

00:24:58.790 --> 00:24:59.440
Yes.

00:25:11.870 --> 00:25:12.790
What do you mean?

00:25:17.030 --> 00:25:18.480
That's what I want to ask you.

00:25:18.820 --> 00:25:20.100
I've been following Fu Sheng,

00:25:20.270 --> 00:25:21.460
just testing him.

00:25:22.590 --> 00:25:24.480
Now I'm sure the jade plate is with him.

00:25:24.600 --> 00:25:26.030
I'll go back to him for dinner later.

00:25:26.440 --> 00:25:26.840
And then...

00:25:26.840 --> 00:25:28.390
Do you think I will still believe you?

00:25:31.970 --> 00:25:32.970
No.

00:25:33.620 --> 00:25:34.810
But it's your only chance.

00:25:44.810 --> 00:25:45.550
You're back.

00:25:46.810 --> 00:25:48.810
Come on then.

00:25:50.810 --> 00:25:51.620
Here.

00:25:52.170 --> 00:25:53.500
Try this.

00:26:02.130 --> 00:26:02.820
Eat.

00:26:03.390 --> 00:26:05.680
Fu Sheng, I want to ask you a favor.

00:26:06.360 --> 00:26:07.390
We're friends.

00:26:07.390 --> 00:26:08.480
You don't have to ask.

00:26:08.720 --> 00:26:09.510
Just say it.

00:26:12.440 --> 00:26:13.600
Can I borrow your

00:26:14.230 --> 00:26:15.600
Bird Jade Plate?

00:26:20.680 --> 00:26:22.510
How do you know the Bird Jade Plate?

00:26:23.840 --> 00:26:25.030
What are you going to do with it?

00:26:26.390 --> 00:26:28.030
Lend it to me or not?

00:26:28.750 --> 00:26:30.080
I've helped you much.

00:26:30.560 --> 00:26:32.750
You can't just pretend to be stupid.

00:26:39.410 --> 00:26:40.930
They all say I'm crazy,

00:26:41.860 --> 00:26:43.770
but I don't think you're any better than me.

00:26:44.170 --> 00:26:45.620
You came to my place to grab things

00:26:46.220 --> 00:26:47.500
and you are still so tough?

00:26:52.530 --> 00:26:53.690
So you won't lend it to me.

00:27:14.460 --> 00:27:15.650
You are on the same side.

00:27:15.650 --> 00:27:16.340
Fu Sheng.

00:27:17.020 --> 00:27:18.380
My final advice to you.

00:27:18.970 --> 00:27:20.300
Hand over the Bird Jade Plate

00:27:20.770 --> 00:27:21.940
and I will let you go.

00:27:23.940 --> 00:27:26.220
I didn't expect you could do this.

00:27:26.730 --> 00:27:27.850
I saw you as a friend.

00:27:28.970 --> 00:27:30.820
But you are here for the plate, too.

00:27:32.220 --> 00:27:33.300
A man is innocent,

00:27:34.220 --> 00:27:35.490
but guilty of possessing a treasure.

00:27:35.940 --> 00:27:37.180
Hand it over.

00:27:37.490 --> 00:27:38.820
Stop hurting innocent people.

00:27:40.890 --> 00:27:42.220
You killed my father?

00:27:44.730 --> 00:27:45.610
Sort of.

00:27:46.490 --> 00:27:49.220
And you also killed those physicians

00:27:49.730 --> 00:27:51.060
and their families?

00:27:51.370 --> 00:27:53.730
Now you know how worthy these things are.

00:27:56.970 --> 00:27:57.820
Yeah.

00:27:59.250 --> 00:28:00.420
And then?

00:28:02.610 --> 00:28:03.970
I'm not giving it to you.

00:28:05.610 --> 00:28:06.890
Then don't blame me

00:28:08.250 --> 00:28:09.420
for being rude.

00:28:21.370 --> 00:28:22.580
You do have some tricks.

00:28:25.610 --> 00:28:26.420
Thank you

00:28:27.250 --> 00:28:28.850
for helping me take down two losers.

00:28:29.850 --> 00:28:30.820
Don't get me wrong.

00:28:31.250 --> 00:28:32.610
I never kill anyone.

00:28:32.650 --> 00:28:34.540
They just fainted.

00:28:36.010 --> 00:28:36.610
Gu Tian.

00:28:44.370 --> 00:28:44.940
Gu Tian.

00:28:45.060 --> 00:28:46.420
We've known each other for a while.

00:28:46.540 --> 00:28:47.700
I'm warning you

00:28:47.970 --> 00:28:49.490
My Ghost Needle has something.

00:28:50.770 --> 00:28:51.650
Ghost Needle?

00:28:53.250 --> 00:28:55.010
Isn't that something from the tale?

00:29:02.970 --> 00:29:03.890
Hurry up.

00:29:04.940 --> 00:29:06.220
You want to die with him?

00:29:07.490 --> 00:29:08.420
Do it!

00:29:35.610 --> 00:29:36.420
Take him!

00:29:39.420 --> 00:29:40.940
It's a mess, huh?

00:29:42.750 --> 00:29:43.890
You little brat,

00:29:44.300 --> 00:29:45.460
dare to fight against us?

00:29:57.190 --> 00:29:58.370
It's a good trick.

00:29:59.860 --> 00:30:01.070
You performed well.

00:30:01.620 --> 00:30:03.670
I have something to confess to you.

00:30:04.100 --> 00:30:04.910
Tell me.

00:30:07.220 --> 00:30:08.980
The man pretending to be a bandit

00:30:09.390 --> 00:30:10.740
came after your Bird Jade Plate.

00:30:11.030 --> 00:30:11.670
Jade plate?

00:30:13.190 --> 00:30:14.370
How did he know it?

00:30:15.500 --> 00:30:16.920
Wait, you know it too?

00:30:17.450 --> 00:30:18.330
You know

00:30:18.500 --> 00:30:19.170
what I

00:30:19.380 --> 00:30:20.660
live on.

00:30:21.860 --> 00:30:24.090
My men heard about these outsiders,

00:30:24.290 --> 00:30:25.420
and they were looking for

00:30:25.420 --> 00:30:27.020
a Bird Jade Plate with a high reward.

00:30:27.570 --> 00:30:28.690
I happened to see it

00:30:29.330 --> 00:30:31.090
in your medicine box,

00:30:32.930 --> 00:30:33.900
and wanted to make a fortune,

00:30:34.500 --> 00:30:36.810
so I planned to steal your plate.

00:30:38.260 --> 00:30:40.380
No wonder you looked so wrong.

00:30:40.380 --> 00:30:41.500
You approached Fu Sheng

00:30:41.500 --> 00:30:43.260
just for that plate thing?

00:30:45.500 --> 00:30:46.620
At first I was.

00:30:47.330 --> 00:30:48.140
But

00:30:48.450 --> 00:30:49.900
I never told anyone

00:30:49.900 --> 00:30:50.970
that you have the jade plate.

00:30:51.170 --> 00:30:52.320
But I didn't expect

00:30:52.570 --> 00:30:53.450
those people

00:30:53.840 --> 00:30:55.530
would be so cruel.

00:30:55.960 --> 00:30:57.000
They killed many people

00:30:57.000 --> 00:30:58.000
for the jade plate.

00:30:59.130 --> 00:31:00.560
I realized something was wrong,

00:31:00.960 --> 00:31:03.040
but he threatened me with more innocent lives,

00:31:03.850 --> 00:31:05.450
so I could only pretend to obey.

00:31:07.590 --> 00:31:08.590
What are you going to do?

00:31:10.310 --> 00:31:11.570
I need your help.

00:31:12.160 --> 00:31:14.160
They disguised as bandits to launch attack,

00:31:14.550 --> 00:31:15.760
so their target is you.

00:31:16.440 --> 00:31:17.760
We can only take the initiative

00:31:18.590 --> 00:31:20.110
and never let him leave Shangyi.

00:31:23.830 --> 00:31:24.590
Alright.

00:31:25.280 --> 00:31:26.070
I'll help you.

00:31:26.820 --> 00:31:30.580
[Fair and Impartial]

00:31:40.190 --> 00:31:42.100
Looks like you picked the wrong path.

00:31:42.780 --> 00:31:44.510
No, you chose the wrong path.

00:31:47.060 --> 00:31:48.300
Within the three-day deadline,

00:31:48.300 --> 00:31:49.580
Fu Sheng fulfilled his mission

00:31:49.780 --> 00:31:52.150
and found the real culprit for the death of the physicians.

00:31:52.620 --> 00:31:55.340
He's also the thief who pretended to be a bandit and kidnapped the caravan

00:31:55.340 --> 00:31:56.860
and attacked us on the way.

00:31:57.540 --> 00:31:58.060
Yes.

00:31:58.430 --> 00:32:00.020
He has just admitted the guilt

00:32:00.020 --> 00:32:01.100
in his confession.

00:32:02.190 --> 00:32:03.230
The taste

00:32:03.340 --> 00:32:04.860
of those medicinal herbs

00:32:05.020 --> 00:32:06.780
changed after they were poisoned.

00:32:07.180 --> 00:32:08.510
And the herbs the physicians used

00:32:08.510 --> 00:32:09.900
to make medicinal tea

00:32:10.170 --> 00:32:11.820
were the poison that killed them.

00:32:13.150 --> 00:32:14.190
Suspect,

00:32:14.540 --> 00:32:15.620
do you plead guilty?

00:32:16.750 --> 00:32:17.750
He's telling the truth.

00:32:17.860 --> 00:32:18.620
Well.

00:32:19.190 --> 00:32:20.390
Since you confessed.

00:32:20.620 --> 00:32:21.470
Guards!

00:32:21.820 --> 00:32:22.950
Let him sign.

00:32:23.300 --> 00:32:24.100
Wait.

00:32:24.860 --> 00:32:25.580
Sir.

00:32:26.190 --> 00:32:28.430
