00:33:02.670 --> 00:33:03.230
Forgive me...

00:33:03.470 --> 00:33:05.020
Untie him, now!

00:33:05.620 --> 00:33:07.880
Magistrate Yang, what do you mean?

00:33:10.060 --> 00:33:11.580
The little Xichuan.

00:33:11.950 --> 00:33:13.150
You're so arrogant.

00:33:13.580 --> 00:33:14.340
How dare you?

00:33:14.340 --> 00:33:15.020
Shut up!

00:33:16.230 --> 00:33:17.020
Princess.

00:33:17.580 --> 00:33:19.750
[Jibei King]
This is the official

00:33:19.750 --> 00:33:21.430
sent by the Jibei Mansion.

00:33:22.230 --> 00:33:23.540
Though Xichuan, to which you belong,

00:33:24.020 --> 00:33:25.910
is also an independent country,

00:33:26.150 --> 00:33:28.390
it is still a small vassal state,

00:33:28.670 --> 00:33:30.300
its strength is far inferior

00:33:30.320 --> 00:33:32.060
to that of Jibei State.

00:33:32.440 --> 00:33:33.160
Princess.

00:33:33.620 --> 00:33:34.910
Don't bring

00:33:34.910 --> 00:33:36.620
unnecessary trouble upon Xichuan.

00:33:38.260 --> 00:33:39.060
What king?

00:33:40.230 --> 00:33:41.190
Jibei King?

00:33:42.990 --> 00:33:44.020
I told you

00:33:44.730 --> 00:33:45.830
you chose the wrong path.

00:33:50.000 --> 00:33:51.530
I was blind.

00:33:51.840 --> 00:33:52.970
I believe you're generous.

00:33:53.000 --> 00:33:54.690
Don't blame me.

00:33:56.370 --> 00:33:57.450
Your look now

00:33:58.170 --> 00:33:59.690
is quite cute.

00:34:00.800 --> 00:34:01.690
We can talk

00:34:02.240 --> 00:34:03.210
later.

00:34:05.170 --> 00:34:06.450
Why did the Jibei King kill my father?

00:34:06.600 --> 00:34:07.930
Fu Sheng, what are you talking about?

00:34:08.650 --> 00:34:10.040
But they did it.

00:34:10.690 --> 00:34:12.040
They also robbed caravans

00:34:12.370 --> 00:34:15.080
and sold the stolen herbs at low prices in Shangyi.

00:34:15.320 --> 00:34:16.000
How dare you?

00:34:16.000 --> 00:34:17.170
He's right.

00:34:33.840 --> 00:34:34.650
Try it.

00:34:41.600 --> 00:34:42.410
Fu Sheng!

00:34:46.000 --> 00:34:46.840
How about it?

00:34:49.520 --> 00:34:50.320
It's not poisonous.

00:34:52.210 --> 00:34:53.410
It doesn't make sense.

00:34:53.730 --> 00:34:54.690
Because this drug

00:34:54.930 --> 00:34:55.890
is not toxic at all.

00:34:58.930 --> 00:34:59.760
There was

00:35:00.410 --> 00:35:02.520
a mysterious group lurking in Jibei for years,

00:35:02.730 --> 00:35:03.760
plotting a rebellion,

00:35:04.410 --> 00:35:05.210
and the mansion

00:35:05.450 --> 00:35:06.560
had long been eyeing them.

00:35:06.930 --> 00:35:08.560
Among them was an important figure,

00:35:09.130 --> 00:35:11.800
who was meticulous and good at disguise.

00:35:12.040 --> 00:35:14.210
He settled in Shangyi as a physician.

00:35:14.600 --> 00:35:17.170
He was poisoned strangely, so he was immune to all poisons.

00:35:17.370 --> 00:35:19.560
Only this medicine called Quexian

00:35:19.600 --> 00:35:21.760
could force out the strange poison in his body.

00:35:21.930 --> 00:35:24.410
Others won't be poisoned if they eat this.

00:35:24.760 --> 00:35:26.690
I wanted to use this trick to lure this man out,

00:35:26.800 --> 00:35:27.600
but he poisoned

00:35:27.600 --> 00:35:28.970
all the physicians

00:35:29.280 --> 00:35:30.410
and confuse the public.

00:35:31.730 --> 00:35:33.080
What a cruel person!

00:35:33.930 --> 00:35:36.040
But they're already dead,

00:35:36.040 --> 00:35:37.730
why does he still hide his identity?

00:35:37.970 --> 00:35:39.600
Because he stole

00:35:40.970 --> 00:35:42.520
an important thing from the mansion.

00:35:48.320 --> 00:35:49.950
Do you know what it is?

00:35:56.830 --> 00:35:57.630
Sir.

00:35:58.470 --> 00:35:59.300
I want an autopsy.

00:35:59.480 --> 00:36:00.280
Well...

00:36:00.550 --> 00:36:01.350
Let him.

00:36:02.480 --> 00:36:04.280
Don't escape with the treasure.

00:36:05.280 --> 00:36:06.240
Send two men to keep an eye on him.

00:36:07.040 --> 00:36:09.520
I'm on it now.

00:36:18.680 --> 00:36:20.310
After examining so many bodies,

00:36:21.150 --> 00:36:22.520
have you found anything?

00:36:26.310 --> 00:36:27.520
What do you mean?

00:36:30.680 --> 00:36:31.480
It's the heart.

00:36:32.720 --> 00:36:34.590
From the extent of damage to their organs,

00:36:34.590 --> 00:36:35.550
I could tell

00:36:35.910 --> 00:36:36.960
they had been poisoned.

00:36:37.480 --> 00:36:39.960
The poison entered the blood from the stomach

00:36:40.070 --> 00:36:41.520
and then to the heart.

00:36:42.310 --> 00:36:44.390
My father's blood contains a strange poison,

00:36:45.480 --> 00:36:48.390
which will be activated once it meets with Quexian,

00:36:48.720 --> 00:36:50.480
and become a deadly poison.

00:36:50.910 --> 00:36:54.110
So my father's organs are least affected,

00:36:55.480 --> 00:36:57.720
which explains why his expression

00:36:58.720 --> 00:37:00.040
is different from those people.

00:37:06.910 --> 00:37:08.760
I don't get it. Why?

00:37:09.680 --> 00:37:10.550
It means

00:37:11.550 --> 00:37:13.000
The man they are looking for is my father.

00:37:14.350 --> 00:37:15.760
He knew he was going to die,

00:37:16.480 --> 00:37:18.390
so he gathered the physicians,

00:37:18.960 --> 00:37:20.150
shared ancient prescriptions,

00:37:21.070 --> 00:37:22.630
and finally killed them.

00:37:23.350 --> 00:37:24.590
But I really don't understand,

00:37:25.630 --> 00:37:27.280
if he knew he was going to die,

00:37:28.110 --> 00:37:29.350
why didn't he take refuge?

00:37:30.110 --> 00:37:31.390
So many lives were gone

00:37:32.520 --> 00:37:33.760
just like that.

00:37:37.300 --> 00:37:39.010
Because of the Bird Jade Plate in your hand.

00:37:40.600 --> 00:37:41.550
The Bird Jade Plate?

00:37:44.700 --> 00:37:45.490
Mr. Ruan.

00:37:46.860 --> 00:37:49.220
I didn't recognize you today.

00:37:49.540 --> 00:37:51.090
Please accept my apologies.

00:37:51.390 --> 00:37:52.820
I will take Fu Sheng away

00:37:53.190 --> 00:37:54.230
after he finishes the autopsy.

00:37:56.860 --> 00:37:57.670
Mr. Ruan.

00:37:58.060 --> 00:37:58.990
I checked

00:37:59.190 --> 00:38:02.100
the warrants issued by the imperial court before,

00:38:02.580 --> 00:38:04.860
and Fu Sheng doesn't seem to be on them.

00:38:09.330 --> 00:38:11.510
What do you mean?

00:38:13.990 --> 00:38:15.590
After all, Fu Sheng

00:38:15.920 --> 00:38:17.970
is a person under my jurisdiction.

00:38:18.370 --> 00:38:21.780
And the murderer of physicians has not been found yet.

00:38:21.980 --> 00:38:24.000
I think it's not the right time

00:38:24.330 --> 00:38:25.890
to let him leave.

00:38:26.740 --> 00:38:28.690
You mean that

00:38:28.930 --> 00:38:30.270
the mansion needs to report to you

00:38:30.410 --> 00:38:32.210
when carrying out missions?

00:38:34.890 --> 00:38:36.140
Let me tell you.

00:38:36.140 --> 00:38:38.300
No matter what his autopsy says,

00:38:38.860 --> 00:38:40.780
I'm taking him away.

00:38:41.540 --> 00:38:42.350
Yes.

00:38:43.140 --> 00:38:45.140
I shouldn't say that.

00:38:47.290 --> 00:38:48.090
Sir.

00:38:49.140 --> 00:38:50.940
She has not woken up since giving birth.

00:38:50.940 --> 00:38:52.290
Her body is burning hot.

00:38:52.690 --> 00:38:54.700
Didn't Fu Sheng prescribe her medicine?

00:38:55.080 --> 00:38:56.020
Ask someone to get it

00:38:56.280 --> 00:38:58.280
and bring it back for her to drink.

00:38:58.630 --> 00:38:59.520
Yes.

00:39:03.100 --> 00:39:03.790
Mr. Ruan.

00:39:04.060 --> 00:39:04.930
Sorry.

00:39:05.020 --> 00:39:07.110
She disturbed our fun.

00:39:07.110 --> 00:39:07.680
Here.

00:39:07.830 --> 00:39:08.680
Let's drink.

00:39:16.550 --> 00:39:17.550
I heard you are quite good

00:39:18.070 --> 00:39:19.630
at being an official.

00:39:32.710 --> 00:39:34.820
I've carried it with me since I was a child.

00:39:35.250 --> 00:39:37.210
What's so special about it?

00:39:48.600 --> 00:39:50.590
My father always had this book in his hand before,

00:39:50.870 --> 00:39:53.270
but it ended up in Zhao Sihu's hands.

00:39:54.030 --> 00:39:55.880
Could the secret be in this book?

